Fourth Department,

October, 1979

(October 26, 1979) R. E. Murphy Real Estate Inc., Respondent, v Manufacturers Hanover Trust Company, Appellant.

Order affirmed, with costs, on the opinion at Special Term, Miller, J. All concur; Hancock, Jr., J. P., not participating. (Appeal from order of Onondaga Supreme Court&emdash;summary judgment.) Present&emdash;Hancock, Jr., J. P., Schnepp, Callahan, Doerr and Witmer, JJ.
